  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nI keep seeing this same log from the same peer\r\n```\r\nfailed to send request a8c5340ce568fc72 to peer 16Uiu2HAm889yCc1ShrApZyM2qCfhtH9ufqWoTEvcfTowVA9HRhtw method=beacon_blocks_by_range, reason=response timeout\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n+ PeerScore system should update score when it see error like that\r\n+ Regular Sync should pick other best peer\r\n\r\nAll code seems to be logical, need to add more log to figure out.",
