    "body": "so everything works according to what was designed. `beacon_blocks_by_range` timeout happens after 4-5 minutes, during that time, there are some `beacon_blocks_by_root` responses and we add 5 score each and that make peer eligible for the next round. Most of the time it switches best peer successfully.\r\n\r\nProbably we should add score based on number of blocks returned too. Right now each `beacon_block_by_root` response is treated with 5 score while it returns only 1 block.",
